# 🌸 Bloom & Grow

A heartwarming habit tracker that turns daily self-care into a journey of personal growth. Complete your habits, watch your Health Points grow, and nurture your relationship with yourself—one task at a time.

![Python Version](https://img.shields.io/badge/python-3.x-blue.svg)
![Tkinter](https://img.shields.io/badge/GUI-Tkinter-green.svg)
![License](https://img.shields.io/badge/license-MIT-lightgrey.svg)

## 📖 About The Project

**Bloom & Grow** was created for a coding competition with the theme of *health*. It's a gamified habit tracker where you:

- ✅ Add daily habits you want to build
- 📋 Check them off as you complete them
- ❤️ Watch your HP (Health Points) increase
- 🌱 (Planned) Watch your flower companion bloom alongside you

Every checked habit adds to your score, and with consistency comes growth—both in the app and in real life.

> *"Complete your checklist everyday and make YOU happy!"*

## 🎮 How It Works

### The Journey Flow

1. **Welcome Screen** - Click the big welcome button to begin
2. **Enter Your Name** - Make it personal
3. **Add Your Habits** - List up to 5 habits you want to track
4. **Daily Check-ins** - Tick off completed tasks to gain HP
5. **New Day** - Hit "TMR" to reset your checklist and continue

### HP Progression

Each completed habit gives you **+10 HP**. The more consistent you are, the fuller your health bar becomes:

| Score | HP Bar Width |
|-------|--------------|
| 10    | ████ (4 units) |
| 20    | ███████ (7 units) |
| 30    | ███████████ (11 units) |
| 40    | ██████████████ (14 units) |
| 50    | ██████████████████ (18 units) |

🚀 Long-term Vision
Mobile App Port - Convert to React Native or Flutter for iOS/Android

Social Features (opt-in):
- Share progress with friends
- Group challenges (e.g., "30-day hydration challenge")
- Accountability partners

Analytics Dashboard:

- Heatmap calendar showing consistency
- Progress charts over weeks/months
- Habit completion trends

Gamification Expansion:

- Daily login rewards
- Achievement badges (7-day streak, 30-day streak, 100 total tasks)
- Level-up system with unlockable flower species

Sound effects and confetti animations for milestones

Accessibility Improvements:
- Dark/light mode toggle
- Screen reader support
- Keyboard shortcuts
- Customizable font sizes

AI Integration (dream big!):

- Personalized habit recommendations based on your patterns
- Smart reminders when you're most likely to complete tasks
- Sentiment analysis from optional daily journal entries

## 🚀 Getting Started

### Prerequisites

- Python 3.x installed on your system
- Tkinter (usually comes pre-installed with Python)

### Installation

1. **Clone the repository**
```bash
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/bloom-and-grow.git
cd bloom-and-grow

### The code currently uses hardcoded image paths. You'll need to update these to match your local setup:
### Update these lines in the code:
bg = PhotoImage(file=r"YOUR_PATH/bg.gif")
title = PhotoImage(file=r"YOUR_PATH/title label.png")
wlcm_btn = PhotoImage(file=r"YOUR_PATH/welcome button.png")
flower = PhotoImage(file=r"YOUR_PATH/flower.png")
note = PhotoImage(file=r"YOUR_PATH/notes.png")
stats = PhotoImage(file=r"YOUR_PATH/name box.png")

### Run
python bloom_and_grow.py

